         <div type="translation" source="#iaph2007">
            <p>The sarcophagus and the burial niche lying below and the place on which the sarcophagus and the niche are located belong to Marcus Aurelius [ . . . .]son of Adrastos son of Kallippos son of Polydeukes.</p>
